<br>
Ah was member o a group tha went inta Chardok t'kill t'Prince. We done well - got oor target wit some problems. Worst was when we got to t'main temple an tried t'enter t'main temple . . . <br>
<br>
Damme entrance had a wonderful (fer tem no fer us) trap . . . <br>
<br>
Stun plus grav-flux every couple ticks . . . (up up an away we went) Anyone near t'damme doorway got nailed an Ah sat an cast HoT an complete heals till me mana was gone . . .<br>
<br>
Tried campin an still wouldna rid us o tha damme curse - tried Cancel Magic . . . an got away from tha doorway an Whack came back . . .<br>
<br>
We used Levitate an it seemed to work on majority o party BUT . . <br>
<br>
When we went around side - - - through the side doors an Ah got near the doorway again (main door) Damme thing hit me again ( I was pressed hard against far wall - could nay get any further away then Ah was) - Ah could no avoid t'trap even wit Levitate on. Almost killed me fer second time.<br>
<br>
QUESTION? Is thar a way past it? A raid is goin t'get seriously disrupted if this hits members -- is going to send everyone inta chaos . . . we were a party o six.<br>
<br>
A party o 16 o 18 o more is going to look like a bunch o scattered chickens if this damme trap hits tem.<br>
<br>
Thankee fer any advice.<br>
<br>
Brell's Blessins<br>
Be well, be safe an be dangerous. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bantizar>Bantizar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/2/03 10:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm59.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=753.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tha damme Grav-flux inta Chardok</span><hr size=1> Am Not sure Of the exact LOC of this trap But I do Know every raid I have been on uses Lev In a couple areas in Chardok Maybe this trap Is the reson why My best advice would be keep Lev on till your done to avoide the trap or have it on when aproaching this trap either way Hope this helps<br>
